.name
AppISizer
.author
Gérard Cornu 
.version
0.61
.reference
AmigaLibDisk802:AppISizer/
0.41
.description
An AppIcon utility to get the size of disks, directories or files.  Gives
the size in bytes, blocks and the actual size occupied.  Now supports 5
tooltypes and command line options for the positioning and replacement of
the internal AppIcon, and for the positioning of the output window.
Requires KickStart 37.175 or higher.  
